snippet.title: Playerless: One Button Adventure - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Game within an abandoned game, Self-aware AIs running wild, One functioning button and Lots of (totally intentional) glitches! 
It's Playerless: One Button Adventure - please, have a trailer! 

Add the game to wishlist: http://bit.ly/Playerless
